subject: Automobile Racing
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: Jeff Burton finally passed Matt Kenseth for the lead on his seventh attempt and won the Dover 400, his first Nascar Nextel Cup victory in nearly five years.
